20have%20been%20introduced%20as%20amendments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20three%20criminal%20laws%20to%20replace%20the%20IPC%2C%20CrPC%20and%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20come%20into%20force%20today%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn90-99%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20so-called%20new%20laws%20are%20a%20cut%2C%20copy%20and%20paste%20job.%20A%20task%20that%20could%20have%20been%20completed%20with%20a%20few%20amendments%20to%20the%20existing%20three%20laws%20has%20been%20turned%20into%20a%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20P.%20Chidambaram%20(%40PChidambaram_IN)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPChidambaram_IN%2Fstatus%2F1807599839326466354%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there%20are%20several%20retrograde%20provisions.%20Some%20changes%20are%20prima%20facie%20unconstitutional.%20MPs%20who%20were%20members%20of%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20have%20poured%20over%20the%20provisions%20and%20written%20detailed%20dissent%20notes%20to%20the%20three%20Bills.%20The%20government%20did%20not%20rebut%20or%20answer%20any%20of%20the%20criticisms%20in%20the%20dissent%20notes.%20There%20was%20no%20worthwhile%20debate%20in%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLaw%20scholars%2C%20Bar%20Associations%2C%20judges%20and%20lawyers%20have%20in%20numerous%20articles%20and%20seminars%20pointed%20out%20the%20grave%20deficiencies%20in%20the%20three%20new%20laws.%20No%20one%20in%20government%20has%20cared%20to%20answer%20the%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20another%20case%20of%20bulldozing%20three%20existing%20laws%20and%20replace%20them%20with%20three%20new%20Bills%20without%20adequate%20discussion%20and%20debate.%20The%20initial%20impact%20will%20be%20to%20throw%20the%20administration%20of%20criminal%20justice%20into%20disarray.%20In%20the%20medium%20term%2C%20numerous%20challenges%20to%20the%20laws%20will%20be%20instituted%20in%20various%20Courts.%20In%20the%20long%20term%2C%20further%20changes%20must%20be%20made%20to%20the%20three%20laws%20to%20bring%20them%20in%20conformity%20with%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20modern%20principles%20of%20criminal%20jurisprudence%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20led%20the%20law%20revision%20exercise%2C%20has%20said%20these%20laws%20%26quot%3Bare%20made%20by%20Indians%2C%20for%20Indians%20and%20by%20an%20Indian%20Parliament%20and%20marks%20the%20end%20of%20colonial%20criminal%20justice%20laws%26quot%3B.%20He%20has%20also%20said%20that%20these%20laws%20were%20not%20just%20about%20changing%20the%20nomenclature%20but%20bringing%20about%20an%20overhaul.%20%26quot%3BSoul%2C%20body%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20new%20laws%20is%20Indian%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20that%20while%20the%20colonial-era%20laws%20focus%20on%20penalty%2C%20these%20laws%20would%20prioritise%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719808080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fb0kdadf_mallikarjun-kharge_625x300_02_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharatiya-nyay-sanhita-new-criminal-laws-congresss-bulldozer-jab-at-centre-as-new-criminal-laws-come-into-force-6007076%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20three%20new%20criminal%20laws%20came%20into%20force%20today%2C%20main%20Opposition%20Congress%20said%20these%20laws%20were%20%26quot%3Bforcibly%26quot%3B%20passed%20by%20suspending%20146%20MPs%20from%20Parliament%20proceedings.%20The%20party%20also%20said%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20these%20laws%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bcut%2C%20copy%20and%20paste%20job%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbha