%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-spacex-falcon-explode-test-accidental-launch-tianbing-tianlong-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B2%20Names%20Shortlisted%26quot%3B%3A%20Amid%20Gambhir-Coach%20Links%2C%20Jay%20Shah's%20Big%20Revelation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20will%20have%20a%20new%20head%20coach%20from%20the%20limited-overs%20series%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20starting%20later%20this%20month%2C%20BCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20said%20on%20Monday%20but%20did%20not%20reveal%20who%20has%20been%20finalised%20to%20succeed%20the%20outgoing%20Rahul%20Dravid.%20Former%20opener%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20is%20expected%20to%20succeed%20Dravid%20as%20the%20India%20head%20coach.%20The%20Cricket%20Advisory%20Committee%20has%20also%20conducted%20the%20interviews%20for%20the%20high-profile%20job%20and%20short-listed%20Gambhir%20and%20former%20India%20women's%20coach%20W%20V%20Raman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20a%20selector%20will%20also%20be%20made%20soon%2C%20said%20Shah%2C%20who%20is%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20with%20the%20India%20squad%20that%20won%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title%20on%20Saturday%2C%20beating%20South%20Africa%20by%20seven%20runs%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20coach%20and%20selector%20appointment%20will%20be%20made%20shortly.%20CAC%20has%20interviewed%20and%20shortlisted%20two%20names%20and%20after%20reaching%20Mumbai%20whatever%20they%20have%20decided%20we%20will%20go%20by%20that.%20VVS%20Laxman%20is%20going%20to%20Zimbabwe%20but%20new%20coach%20will%20join%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20told%20select%20media%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Zimbabwe%20tour%20beginning%20July%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20is%20due%20to%20tour%20Sri%20Lanka%20for%20three%20T20Is%20and%20as%20many%20ODIs%20starting%20July%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeniors'%20presence%20helped%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20showed%20his%20elation%20after%20India%20won%20an%20ICC%20title%20after%2011%20years%20here%20on%20Saturday.%20He%20praised%20the%20efforts%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20who%20played%20a%20match-winning%20knock%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20stalwarts%20announced%20their%20retirement%20from%20T20Is%20after%20the%20triumph%20and%20were%20joined%20by%20all-rounder%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20in%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20the%20format%20a%20day%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20same%20captain%20last%20year%20and%20same%20here%20in%20Barbados.%20We%20won%20all%20games%20except%20the%20final%20in%202023%20as%20Australia%20played%20better.%20This%20time%20we%20worked%20even%20harder%20and%20played%20better%20to%20win%20the%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20other%20teams%2C%20experience%20counts.%20From%20Rohit%20to%20Virat%2C%20all%20excelled.%20Experience%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20difference%2C%20in%20World%20Cups%20you%20can't%20experiment%20much%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20good%20player%20knows%20when%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20the%20game%2C%20we%20saw%20that%20yesterday.%20You%20look%20at%20Rohit's%20strike%20rate%2C%20it%20is%20better%20than%20a%20lot%20of%20young%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20he%20see%20the%20transition%20panning%20out%20following%20the%20retirement%20of%20Rohit%2C%20Kohli%20and%20Jadeja%3F%20%26quot%3BTransition%20has%20already%20happened%20with%20three%20greats%20retiring%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20who%20had%20built%20a%20reputation%20of%20losing%20the%20big%20finals%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20finally%20ended%20their%20title%20drought%20after%20losing%20two%20ICC%20finals%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months%20and%20Shah%20hoped%20the%20winning%20run%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20want%20India%20to%20win%20all%20the%20titles.%20We%20have%20the%20biggest%20bench%20strength%2C%20only%20three%20players%20from%20this%20team%20are%20going%20to%20Zimbabwe.%20We%20can%20field%20three%20teams%20if%20the%20need%20arises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20this%20team%20is%20progressing%2C%20our%20target%20is%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20and%20Champions%20Trophy.%20There%20will%20be%20a%20similar%20squad%20playing%20there.%20The%20seniors%20will%20be%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Hardik%20Pandya's%20all-round%20performance%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20chances%20of%20him%20taking%20over%20captaincy%20from%20Rohit%2C%20Shah%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BCaptaincy%20will%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20selectors%20and%20we%20will%20announce%20it%20after%20discussing%20with%20them.%20You%20asked%20about%20Hardik%2C%20there%20were%20lot%20of%20questions%20over%20his%20form%20but%20we%20and%20selectors%20showed%20faith%20in%20him%20and%20he%20proved%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20A%20to%20tour%20Australia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20also%20confirmed%20that%20an%20A%20team%20will%20be%20travelling%20to%20Australia%20later%20in%20the%20year%20ahead%20of%20the%20five%20Tests%20Down%20Under.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20is%20planning%20a%20felicitation%20after%20reaching%20India%20but%20the%20Hurricane%20warning%20has%20shut%20down%20the%20airport%20in%20Barbados%20indefinitely%2C%20leaving%20the%20victorious%20squad%20stranded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20you%20we%20are%20also%20stuck%20here.%20After%20the%20travel%20plans%20are%20clear%2C%20we%20will%20think%20about%20the%20felicitation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicate