0Chaplin)%2C%20and%20his%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Targaryen%20civil%20war%2C%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BDance%20of%20Dragons%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20only%20just%20starting%20to%20escalate%20at%20the%20start%20of%20season%20two.%20It%20could%20be%20some%20time%20before%20audiences%20see%20Cole's%20death%20in%20live%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20season%20two%20airs%20Sundays%20at%209%20p.m.%20ET%20on%20HBO%20and%20is%20streaming%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20sponsored%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dfed657e5d456898628c785351016f7b12b4d269a5d17af0f15435159aef229d0%26postID%3D667ecca485b49b35b2851d69%26postSlug%3Dhouse-of-the-dragon-criston-cole-death-book-2024-6%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.max.com%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EMax%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-of-the-dragon-criston-cole-death-book-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719804662000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667ee9db50b021b5caea8720%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-of-the-dragon-criston-cole-death-book-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Criston%20Cole%20(Fabien%20Frankel)%20gets%20chased%20by%20a%20dragon%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20season%20two%2C%20episode%20three.%20Here's%20how%20he%20dies%20in%20the%20book.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ejacobs%40insider.com%20(Eammon%20Jacobs)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-of-the-dragon-criston-cole-death-book-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22France%20polls%3A%20Paris%20on%20edge%20as%20'militant%20activists'%20take%20to%20streets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719804238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111392077%2Cimgsize-56984.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrance-parliamentary-elections-far-right-national-rally-party-marine-le-pen-macron%2Farticleshow%2F111392045.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20far-right%20National%20Rally%20leaped%20into%20a%20strong%20lead%20Sunday%20in%20France's%20first%20round%20of%20legislative%20elections%2C%20polling%20agencies%20projected%2C%20bringing%20the%20party%20closer%20to%20being%20able%20to%20form%20a%20government%20in%20round%20two%20and%20dealing%20a%20major%20slap%20to%20centrist%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20his%20risky%20decision%20to%20call%20the%20surprise%20ballot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrance-parliamentary-elections-far-right-national-rally-party-marine-le-pen-macron%2Farticleshow%2F111392045.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Macron's%20Party%20Headed%20For%20Defeat%20After%20Strong%20Showing%20By%20France's%20Far%20Right%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrance's%20far%20right%20was%20on%20Sunday%20eyeing%20a%20historic%20chance%20to%20form%20a%20government%20and%20claim%20the%20post%20of%20prime%20minister%20after%20winning%20the%20first%20round%20of%20legislative%20elections%20with%20the%20centrist%20forces%20of%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20coming%20in%20only%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20remained%20unclear%20if%20the%20far-right%20National%20Rally%20(RN)%20party%20of%20Marine%20Le%20Pen%20would%20win%20the%20absolute%20majority%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20new%20National%20Assembly%20in%20the%20July%207%20second%20round.%20That%20is%20what%20it%20would%20need%20to%20be%20certain%20of%20taking%20power%20and%20for%20Le%20Pen's%20protege%20Jordan%20Bardella%2C%2028%2C%20to%20become%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20had%20stunned%20the%20nation%20and%20baffled%20even%20some%20allies%20by%20calling%20snap%20polls%20after%20the%20RN%20trounced%20his%20centrist%20forces%20in%20European%20Parliament%20elections%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20gamble%20risks%20backfiring%2C%20with%20Macron's%20alliance%20now%20expected%20to%20win%20a%20far%20smaller%20minority%20contingent%20in%20parliament.%20That%20would%20make%20the%20president%20a%20far%20less%20powerful%20figure%20for%20the%20remaining%20three%20years%20of%20his%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProjections%20from%20prominent%20French%20polling%20firms%20gave%20the%20RN%2033.2-33.5%20percent%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20compared%20to%2028.1-28.5%20percent%20for%20the%20left-wing%20New%20Popular%20Front%20alliance%2C%20and%2021.0-22.1%20percent%20for%20Macron's%20centrist%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polling%20agencies%20projected%20this%20would%20give%20the%20RN%20a%20majority%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20577-seat%20National%20Assembly%20after%20the%20second%20round.%20But%20it%20was%20far%20from%20clear%20the%20party%20would%20garner%20the%20289%20seats%20needed%20for%20an%20absolute%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20projections%20varied%20sharply%2C%20with%20Ipsos%20forecasting%20230-280%20seats%2C%20Ifop%20240-270%20and%20Elabe%20the%20only%20organisation%20to%20put%20it%20in%20the%20range%20of%20an%20absolute%20majority%20on%20260-310%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Macron%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bbroad%26quot%3B%20alliance%20against%20the%20far%20right%20in%20the%20second%20round%2C%20which%20will%20see%20run-off%20votes%20where%20there%20was%20no%20outright%20winner%20in%20the%20first%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leftwing%20alliance%20and%20the%20president's%20camp%20will%20be%20hoping%20that%20tactical%20voting%20to%20prevent%20RN%20candidates%20winning%20seats%20will%20leave%20it%20short%20of%20the%20absolute%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20Prime%20Minister%20Gabriel%20Attal%2C%20who%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20forced%20to%20resign%20after%20the%20second%20round%2C%20warned%20the%20far%20right%20was%20now%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bgates%20of%20power%26quot%3B.%20The%20RN%20should%20not%20get%20a%20%26quot%3Bsingle%20vote%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20second%20round%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seven%20days%20to%20spare%20France%20from%20catastrophe%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Raphael%20Glucksmann%2C%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20the%20left-wing%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Prime%20minister%20of%20all%20French'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20French%20facing%20their%20most%20polarising%20choices%20in%20recent%20history%2C%20turnout%20soared%20to%2065%20percent%2C%20way%20above%20the%20turnout%20in%202022%20polls%20of%20just%2047.5%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20said%20the%20high%20turnout%20in%20the%20first%20round%20spoke%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20importance%20of%20this%20vote%20for%20all%20our%20compatriots%20and%20the%20desire%20to%20clarify%20the%20political%20situation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrival%20of%20anti-immigration%20and%20eurosceptic%20RN%20in%20government%20would%20be%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20French%20modern%20history%20and%20be%20the%20first%20time%20a%20far-right%20force%20has%20taken%20power%20in%20the%20country%20since%20World%20War%20II%20when%20it%20was%20occupied%20by%20Nazi%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20is%20won%20and%20the%20second%20round%20is%20decisive%2C%26quot%3B%20Le%20Pen%2C%20who%20has%20long%20worked%20to%20distance%20the%20party%20from%20its%20extremist%20origins%2C%20told%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20an%20absolute%20majority%20so%20that%20Jordan%20Bardella%20is%20in%20eight%20days%20named%20prime%20minister%20by%20Emmanuel%20Macron.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBardella%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bprime%20minister%20of%20all%20French%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20create%20a%20tense%20period%20of%20%26quot%3Bcohabitation%26quot%3B%20with%20Macron%2C%20who%20has%20vowed%20to%20serve%20out%20his%20term%20until%202027.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBardella%20has%20said%20he%20will%20only%20form%20a%20government%20if%20the%20RN%20wins%20an%20absolute%20majority%20in%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Heavy%20defeat'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alternative%20is%20months%20of%20political%20paralysis%20and%20negotiations%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20for%20a%20sustainable%20government%20that%20can%20survive%20no-confidence%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHard-left%20leader%20Jean-Luc%20Melenchon%20said%20Macron's%20centrist%20alliance%20had%20suffered%20a%20%26quot%3Bheavy%20and%20undisputable%26quot%3B%20defeat%20in%20the%20snap%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERisk%20analysis%20firm%20Eurasia%20Group%20said%20the%20RN%20now%20looked%20%26quot%3Blikely%26quot%3B%20to%20fall%20short%20of%20an%20absolute%20majority.%20France%20was%20facing%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%2012%20months%20with%20a%20rancorously%20blocked%20National%20Assembly%20and%20--%20at%20best%20--%20a%20technocratic%20government%20of%20'national%20unity'%20with%20limited%20capacity%20to%20govern%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron's%20decision%20to%20call%20the%20snap%20vote%20sparked%20uncertainty%20in%20Europe's%20second-biggest%20economy.%20The%20Paris%20stock%20exchange%20suffered%20its%20biggest%20monthly%20decline%20in%20two%20years%20in%20June%2C%20dropping%20by%206.4%20percent%2C%20according%20to%20figures%20released%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turmoil%20also%20risks%20undermining%20Macron's%20stature%20as%20an%20international%20leader%20taking%20a%20prime%20role%20in%20helping%20Ukraine%20fight%20the%20Russian%20invasion.%20In%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20second%20round%20he%20is%20due%20to%20attend%20the%20NATO%20summit%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20daily%20Liberation%20urged%20voters%20to%20unite%20to%20halt%20the%20march%20of%20the%20far-right.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20shock%2C%20form%20a%20block%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20newspaper%20said%20on%20its%20Monday%20front%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719803880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F4bm8n8so_macron-_625x300_01_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Femmanuel-macron-france-snap-election-2024-setback-for-macron-as-french-far-right-wins-first-round-in-france-election-6006423%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22France's%20far%20right%20was%20on%20Sunday%20eyeing%20a%20historic%20chance%20to%20form%20a%20government%20and%20claim%20the%20post%20of%20prime%20minister%20after%20winning%20the%20first%20round%20of%20legislative%20elections%20with%20the%20centrist%20forces%20of%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20coming%20in%20only%20third.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Femmanuel-macron-france-snap-election-2024-setback-for-macron-as-french-far-right-wins-first-round-in-france-election-6006423%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Femmanuel-macron-france-snap-election-2024-setback-for-macron-as-french-far-right-wins-first-round-in-france-election-6006423%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Femmanuel-macron-france-snap-election-2024-setback-for-macron-as-french-far-right-wins-first-round-in-france-election-6006423%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Colonial-Era%20IPC%20Out%2C%20New%20Criminal%20Laws%20Take%20Effect%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Adhiniyam%20will%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20and%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20laws%20were%20changed%20to%20ensure%20speedier%20justice%20and%20be%20in%20sync%20with%20this%20day%20and%20age%20and%20the%20new%20forms%20of%20crime%20that%20occur%2C%20the%20government%20has%20said.%20Judgments%20are%20now%20required%20within%2045%20days%20of%20completion%20of%20trial%20and%20charges%20framed%20within%2060%20days%20of%20first%20hearing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20laws%20will%20allow%20any%20person%20to%20file%20a%20Zero%20FIR%20at%20any%20police%20station%2C%20regardless%20of%20jurisdiction%3B%20it%20will%20permit%20online%20registration%20of%20police%20complaints%20and%20electronic%20serving%20of%20summons.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20make%20videography%20of%20crime%20scenes%20mandatory%20for%20all%20heinous%20crimes.%20Summonses%20can%20be%20served%20electronically%2C%20expediting%20the%20legal%20processes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20said%20the%20change%20was%20made%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bspeedy%20justice%20and%20justice%20to%20all%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%20Proper%20implementation%20of%20these%20laws%20will%20require%20training%20and%20forensic%20teams%2C%20whose%20visits%20have%20been%20made%20mandatory%20for%20offences%20carrying%20a%20sentence%20of%20seven%20years%20or%20more%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENew%20provisions%20have%20been%20made%20in%20view%20of%20emerging%20crimes%20like%20gang%20rapes%2C%20killing%20by%20mobs%2C%20false%20promise%20of%20marriage%20and%20others.%20%26quot%3BThis%20will%20increase%20the%20demand%20for%20forensic%20experts%20across%20the%20country%2C%20which%20the%20NFSU%20(National%20Forensic%20Science%20University)%20will%20cater%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20has%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20NFSU%20was%20taken%20forward%20as%20the%20new%20laws%20were%20being%20framed%2C%20he%20added.%20Campuses%20of%20this%20university%20have%20been%20opened%20in%209%20states%2C%20which%20will%20be%20expanded%20to%2016%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20maintain%20the%20decision%20to%20implement%20the%20new%20criminal%20laws%20from%20July%201%20has%20been%20taken%20in%20haste.%20More%20consultation%20was%20required%20before%20enforcing%20them%2C%20the%20party%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20urged%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20defer%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bhurriedly%20passed%26quot%3B%20laws.%20Parliament%2C%20she%20said%2C%20could%20then%20review%20them%20afresh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThese%20laws%20signify%20a%20watershed%20moment%20for%20our%20society%20because%20no%20law%20affects%20the%20day-to-day%20conduct%20of%20our%20society%20like%20the%20criminal%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20has%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719803820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F8hulrkec_jail-generic_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcolonial-era-ipc-out-new-criminal-laws-take-effect-today-10-points-6005426%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20criminal%20justice%20system%20will%20undergo%20a%20complete%20overhaul%20today%20with%20three%20fresh%20criminal%20codes%20replacing%20the%20full%20set%20of%20British-era%20laws%2C%20including%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcolonial-era-ipc-out-new-criminal-laws-take-effect-today-10-points-6005426%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com