-that-are-far-more-fitting-mother-of-war-hero-questions-decision-to-award-prince-harry-the-pat-tillman-award%2Famp_articleshow%2F111390883.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20Didn't%20Want%20To%20Retire%20From%20T20Is%2C%20But%20%26quot%3BSituation%20Was...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20callled%20time%20on%20his%20T20I%20career%20after%20guiding%20the%20team%20to%20its%20second%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20format%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20the%20perfect%20time%20to%20%26quot%3Bsay%20goodbye%26quot%3B.%20Rohit%20made%20the%20announcement%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20after%20his%20long-time%20teammate%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20brought%20down%20curtains%20on%20his%20fabled%20career%20minutes%20after%20India%20defeated%20South%20Africa%20by%20seven%20runs%20at%20the%20Kensington%20Oval%2C%20Barbados%20in%20the%20final.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20my%20last%20game%20as%20well.%20No%20better%20time%20to%20say%20goodbye.%20I%20wanted%20this%20(trophy)%20badly.%20It's%20very%20hard%20to%20put%20in%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20told%20at%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20what%20I%20wanted%20and%20it%20happened.%20I%20was%20very%20desperate%20for%20this%20in%20my%20life.%20Happy%20that%20we%20crossed%20the%20line%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20had%20led%20India%20in%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup%20where%20the%20team%20was%20ousted%20in%20the%20semifinals%20by%20eventual%20champions%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20India%20reached%20the%20final%20of%20the%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%20under%20h