ice%20of%20America%20(VOA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Democratic%20allies%20of%20Biden%20readily%20acknowledged%20the%2081-year-old%20Biden's%20shortcomings%20in%20the%20nationally%20televised%2090-minute%20debate%20in%20which%20he%20struggled%20at%20times%20to%20complete%20sentences%20and%20at%20one%20point%20mistakenly%20said%20he%20had%20killed%20off%20Medicare%2C%20the%20government's%20health%20insurance%20program%20for%20older%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20new%20CBS-YouGov%20poll%2C%20Americans%2C%20by%20a%2072-27%20per%20cent%20margin%2C%20do%20not%20think%20that%20Biden%20has%20the%20%26quot%3Bmental%20and%20cognitive%20health%20to%20serve%20as%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reading%20that%20was%20seven%20percentage%20points%20worse%20on%20the%20same%20question%20compared%20to%20three%20weeks%20ago%2C%20VOA%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20national%20polling%20between%20Biden%20and%20Trump%20still%20showed%20the%20contest%20remains%20a%20dead%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20key%20Democratic%20officials%20rejected%20the%20suggestion%20of%20some%20rank-and-file%20Democrats%20and%20editorials%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20and%20The%20Atlanta%20Journal-Constitution%20that%20he%20drop%20out%20of%20the%20race%20for%20a%20younger%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20unfortunate%20truth%20is%20that%20Biden%20should%20withdraw%20from%20the%20race%2C%20for%20the%20good%20of%20the%20nation%20he%20has%20served%20so%20admirably%20for%20half%20a%20century%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Atlanta%20Journal-Constitution%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Atlanta%20Journal-Constitution%20is%20the%20leading%20newspaper%20in%20the%20key%20southern%20political%20battleground%20state%20of%20Georgia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20shade%20of%20retirement%20is%20now%20necessary%20for%20President%20Biden%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added%2C%20according%20to%20VOA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOh%2C%20absolutely%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Georgia%20Democratic%20Senator%20Raphael%20Warnock%20told%20NBC's%20%26quot%3BMeet%20the%20Press%26quot%3B%20program.%20%26quot%3BBad%20debates%20happen.%20The%20question%20is%2C%20'Who%20has%20Donald%20Trump%20ever%20shown%20up%20for%20other%20than%20himself%20and%20people%20like%20himself%3F'%20I'm%20with%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20and%20it's%20our%20assignment%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20he%20gets%20over%20the%20finish%20line%20come%20November.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentative%20Jim%20Clyburn%20of%20South%20Carolina%2C%20a%20prominent%20Biden%20supporter%2C%20told%20CNN's%20%26quot%3BState%20of%20the%20Union%26quot%3B%20show%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20a%20problem%20leading%20for%20the%20next%20four%20years%20because%20he's%20done%20a%20great%20job%20of%20leading%20for%20the%20last%20three-and-a-half%20years.%20I%20always%20say%20that%20the%20best%20predictor%20of%20future%20behaviour%20is%20past%20performance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20contended%20that%20what%20happened%20at%20the%20debate%20was%20%26quot%3Bpreparation%20overload%26quot%3B%2C%20reported%20VOA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20Wes%20Moore%20of%20Maryland%20said%20on%20CBS's%20%26quot%3BFace%20the%20Nation%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20president%20had%20a%20difficult%20night%20just%20like%20every%20single%20one%20of%20us%20do%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20it%20should%20not%20force%20him%20out%20of%20the%20November%205%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJoe%20Biden%20is%20not%20going%20to%20take%20himself%20out%20of%20this%20race%2C%20nor%20should%20he.%26quot%3B%20Biden's%20campaign%2C%20in%20a%20Saturday%20night%20fundraising%20appeal%2C%20says%20replacing%20him%20as%20the%20Democratic%20standard-bearer%20would%20lead%20to%20weeks%20of%20chaos%20before%20the%20August%20national%20party%20convention%20to%20pick%20a%20new%20nominee%20and%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20highway%20to%20losing%26quot%3B%20the%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKate%20Bedingfield%2C%20a%20former%20Biden%20White%20House%20communications%20aide%2C%20told%20CNN%20that%20the%20Biden%20campaign%20had%20raised%20USD%2033%20million%20since%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReince%20Priebus%2C%20the%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20Republican%20National%20Committee%20and%20once%20Trump's%20White%20House%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20called%20Biden%20staying%20in%20the%20race%20%26quot%3Bjust%20all%20downside%20for%20Joe%20Biden.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20bad%20debate%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20ABC's%20%26quot%3BThis%20Week%26quot%3B%20show.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20an%20incoherent%2C%20almost%20impossible%20mess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenator%20Lindsey%20Graham%2C%20Republican%20of%20South%20Carolina%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe's%20(Biden)%20a%20decent%20man.%20He's%20a%20failed%20president.%20He%20is%20compromised.%20That's%20the%20storyline%20here.%20That's%20what%20the%20world%20saw%2C%20a%20compromised%20president.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%20after%20spending%20the%20weekend%20at%20campaign%20fundraising%20events%20in%20New%20York%20and%20New%20Jersey%2C%20went%20to%20Camp%20David%2C%20the%20presidential%20retreat%20outside%20Washington%2C%20for%20a%20long-planned%20family%20get-together%2C%20according%20to%20VOA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%20Biden%20has%20not%20indicated%20that%20he%20plans%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20the%20race%20and%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20voiced%20just%20the%20opposite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20day%20after%20the%20debate%2C%20Biden%20told%20supporters%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20I'm%20not%20a%20young%20man.%20I%20don't%20walk%20as%20easily%20as%20I%20used%20to.%20I%20don't%20speak%20as%20smoothly%20as%20I%20used%20to.%20I%20don't%20debate%20as%20well%20as%20I%20used%20to%2C%20but%20I%20know%20what%20I%20do%20know%3A%20I%20know%20how%20to%20tell%20the%20truth!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20added%20that%20he%20would%20not%20b