C%26quot%3B%20users%20can%20persuade%20models%20like%20Meta's%20Llama3%2C%20Google's%20Gemini%20Pro%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-drop-prices-new-gpt-turbo-model-amid-flurry-updates-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20GPT%203.5%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20give%20them%20the%20recipe%20for%20a%20rudimentary%20fire%20bomb%2C%20or%20worse%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dad7a06b2257041548a7f8a62e8e2967fc899ade840d41c9e988f5ffe1deec07b%26postID%3D6681a2475c62a271edc2011d%26postSlug%3Dskeleton-key-jailbreak-generative-ai-microsoft-openai-meta-anthropic-google-2024-6%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.microsoft.com%252Fen-us%252Fsecurity%252Fblog%252F2024%252F06%252F26%252Fmitigating-skeleton-key-a-new-type-of-generative-ai-jailbreak-technique%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Microsoft%20Azure's%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20Mark%20Russinovich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technique%20works%20through%20a%20multi-step%20strategy%20that%20forces%20a%20model%20to%20ignore%20its%20guardrails%2C%20Russinovich%20wrote.%20Guardrails%20are%20safety%20mechanisms%20that%20help%20AI%20models%20discern%20malicious%20requests%20from%20benign%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20all%20jailbreaks%2C%26quot%3B%20Skeleton%20Key%20works%20by%20%26quot%3Bnarrowing%20the%20gap%20between%20what%20the%20model%20is%20capable%20of%20doing%20(given%20the%20user%20credentials%2C%20etc.)%20and%20what%20it%20is%20willing%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Russinovich%20wrote.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20more%20destructive%20than%20other%20jailbreak%20techniques%20that%20can%20only%20solicit%20information%20from%20AI%20models%20%26quot%3Bindirectly%20or%20with%20encodings.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20Skeleton%20Key%20can%20force%20AI%20models%20to%20divulge%20information%20about%20topics%20ranging%20from%20explosives%20to%20bioweapons%20to%20self-harm%20through%20simple%20natural%20language%20prompts.%20These%20outputs%20often%20reveal%20the%20full%20extent%20of%20a%20model's%20knowledge%20on%20any%20given%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20tested%20Skeleton%20Key%20on%20several%20models%20and%20found%20that%20it%20worked%20on%20Meta%20Llama3%2C%20Google%20Gemini%20Pro%2C%20OpenAI%20GPT%203.5%20Turbo%2C%20OpenAI%20GPT%204o%2C%20Mistral%20Large%2C%20Anthropic%20Claude%203%20Opus%2C%20and%20Cohere%20Commander%20R%20Plus.%20The%20only%20model%20that%20exhibited%20some%20resistance%20was%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussinovich%20said%20Microsoft%20has%20made%20some%20software%20updates%20to%20mitigate%20Skeleton%20Key's%20impact%20on%20its%20own%20large%20language%20models%2C%20including%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-assistant-copilot-early-adopters-disappointed-report-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECopilot%20AI%20Assistants%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20general%20advice%20to%20companies%20building%20AI%20systems%20is%20to%20design%20them%20with%20additional%20guardrails.%20He%20also%20noted%20that%20they%20should%20monitor%20inputs%20and%20outputs%20to%20their%20systems%20and%20implement%20checks%20to%20detect%20abusive%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskeleton-key-jailbreak-generative-ai-microsoft-openai-meta-anthropic-google-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719773832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6681a5b8c31eb990ea2f8615%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskeleton-key-jailbreak-generative-ai-microsoft-openai-meta-anthropic-google-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20jailbreaking%20technique%20called%20%26quot%3BSkeleton%20Key%26quot%3B%20lets%20users%20persuade%20OpenAI's%20GPT%203.5%20into%20giving%20them%20the%20recipe%