%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20double-edged%20sword.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bcg.com%2Fpublications%2F2024%2Fai-at-work-friend-foe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%2C%20workers'%20confidence%20in%20generative%20AI%20has%20grown%20over%20the%20past%20year%20%E2%80%94%20but%20so%20has%20their%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBCG%20surveyed%20over%2013%2C100%20respondents%2C%20evenly%20divided%20between%20frontline%2C%20managerial%2C%20and%20leadership%20roles.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20found%20that%20confidence%20in%20generative%20AI%20surged%2016%25%20between%202023%20to%202024%2C%20but%20that%20anxiety%20did%20too%3A%20about%205%25.%20The%20percentage%20of%20workers%20who%20worry%20that%20AI%20will%20eliminate%20their%20jobs%20in%20the%20next%20decade%20has%20jumped%20significantly%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EFrontline%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20those%20without%20managerial%20responsibilities%20%E2%80%94%20are%20most%20anxious%20about%20the%20technology%2C%20with%2022%25%20saying%20they%20were%20worried%20about%20it%20compared%20to%2018%25%20of%20managers%20and%2015%25%20of%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20clear%20knowledge%20gap%20between%20executives%20and%20their%20employees%2C%20too.%20Only%2028%25%20of%20frontline%20workers%20reported%20being%20trained%20on%20how%20the%20technology%20will%20impact%20their%20jobs%2C%20compared%20to%2030%25%20of%20managers%20and%2050%25%20of%20leaders.%20Frontline%20workers%20say%20their%20top%20three%20concerns%20about%20generative%20AI%20are%20that%20they%20haven't%20been%20given%20enough%20time%20to%20learn%20about%20it%2C%20sufficient%20training%20opportunities%2C%20or%20knowledge%20of%20when%20to%20use%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20undoubtedly%20a%20shortage%20in%20AI%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20Alex%20Libre%2C%20cofounder%20and%20principal%20recruiter%20of%20Einstellen%20Talent%2C%20a%20service%20that%20matches%20job%20candidates%20with%20generative%20AI%20startups%2C%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-are-teaching-workers-ai-skills-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20are%20trying%20to%20address%20the%20gap%20by%20offering%20workers%20upskilling%20programs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPwC%2C%20the%20consulting%20firm%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpwc-training-workers-ai-usage-quickly-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erolled%20out%20a%20training%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%2075%2C000%20workers%20across%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Mexico%20to%20teach%20employees%20how%20to%20incorporate%20the%20technology%20into%20their%20daily%20work.%20The%20goal%20is%20for%20all%2075%2C000%20employees%20to%20%26quot%3Bknow%20how%20to%20use%20it%20and%20start%20to%20be%20able%20to%20comment%20on%20it%20in%20a%20very%20informed%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Shannon%20Schuyler%2C%20US%20chief%20purpose%20and%20inclusion%20officer%20at%20PwC%2C%20previously%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20say%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20free%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-chatgpt-at-work-job-save-time-ai-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehumans%20to%20do%20more%20meaningful%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20even%20get%20more%20fulfillment%20from%20their%20jobs.%20But%20the%20worry%20right%20now%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-replace-your-job-increase-productivitiy-angus-deaton-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20might%20draw%20a%20line%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20haves%20and%20have-nots%3A%20Those%20who%20know%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20and%20keep%20jobs%20and%20those%20who%20don't%20and%20lose%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20