s%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Rogue's%20only%20powerplant%20option%20is%20Nissan's%20KR15DDT%20variable%20compression%20engine.%20This%20gutsy%20three-cylinder%20engine%20produces%20201%20horsepower%20and%20225%20lb-ft%20of%20torque%2C%20which%20are%20substantial%20improvements%20over%20the%20previous%202.5-liter%20four-cylinder's%20181%20horsepower%20and%20181%20lb-ft%20of%20torque.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20Rogues%20send%20their%20power%20to%20the%20wheels%20through%20a%20continuously%20variable%20transmission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three-cylinder%20engine%20is%20equipped%20with%20Nissan's%20unique%20variable%20compression%20technology%2C%20which%20can%20vary%20the%20compression%20ratio%20within%20the%20engine%20from%208%3A1%20under%20hard%20acceleration%20up%20to%2014%3A1%20for%20more%20efficient%20operation%20while%20cruising%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENissan%20debuted%20the%20technology%20in%20its%20Infiniti%20QX50%20luxury%20SUV%20back%20in%202019%2C%20but%20it%20has%20since%20been%20deployed%20in%20mass-market%20models%20like%20the%20Rogue%20and%20the%20Nissan%20Altima%20sedan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SUV%20delivered%20solid%20fuel%20economy%20figures%20of%2028%20mpg%20city%2C%2034%20mpg%20highway%2C%20and%2031%20mpg%20combined.%20I%20got%20just%20over%2030%20mpg%20in%20my%20120-mile%20test%20loop%2C%20which%20consisted%20of%20city%20and%20highway%20driving%20in%20the%20searing%20Georgia%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Rogue%20is%20terrific%20to%20drive.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20cabin%20of%20a%202024%20Nissan%20Rogue%20SL%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667e2d6540cf2af6e4f68255%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Rogue's%20front%20cabin.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Rogue%20delivers%20a%20friendly%20and%20pleasant%20driving%20experience.%20The%20turbocharged%20engine%20sends%20strong%20power%20throughout%20the%20rev%20range.%20The%20three-cylinders%20remained%20remarkably%20quiet%20and%20smooth%20even%20under%20the%20strain%20of%20hard%20acceleration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20engine%20is%20somewhat%20let%20down%20by%20the%20inconsistent%20performance%20of%20the%20CVT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20using%20a%20CVT%20instead%20of%20a%20traditional%20automatic%20transmission%20trades%20all-out%20performance%20for%20smoothness%20and%20fuel%20efficiency.%20While%20it%20does%20help%20the%20Rogue%20deliver%20in%20terms%20of%20fuel%20economy%2C%20it%20has%20pre-programmed%20shift%20points%20designed%20to%20mimic%20that%20of%20a%20regular%20automatic%20transmission.%20This%20creates%20an%20almost%20rubbery%20feeling%20in%20the%20throttle%20under%20hard%20throttle%20application%20that%20feels%20like%20it%20slows%20down%20the%20acceleration%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20really%20blame%20Nissan%20for%20this.%20We%2C%20consumers%2C%20demanded%20the%20addition%20of%20these%20shift%20points%20because%20many%20found%20the%20consistent%20hum%20of%20an%20engine%20at%20a%20constant%20RPM%20to%20be%20disconcerting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.motortrend.com%2Fcars%2Fnissan%2Frogue%2F2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMotor%20Trend%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%202024%20Nissan%20Rogue%20can%20do%200-60%20mph%20in%208.4%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EInside%2C%20the%20Rogue%20offers%20its%20occupants%20a%20really%20nice%20place%20to%20be.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20dash%20in%20a%202024%20Nissan%20Rogue%20SL%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667e28f9d1c84a0eaca89369%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Rogue's%20front%20dash.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInterior%20ergonomics%20are%20excellent%20and%20everything%20feels%20well%20put%20together.%20My%20test%20car%20had%20more%20than%208%2C000%20miles%20on%20the%20clock%2C%20and%20yet%20it%20felt%20as%20solid%20as%20new.%20There%20were%20no%20squeaks%20or%20rattles%20to%20report.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20major%20complaint%20with%20the%20cabin%20is%20the%20quality%20of%20some%20of%20the%20plastic%20trim%20pieces.%20They%20just%20felt%20cheap%2C%20especially%20for%20a%20%2440%2C000%20vehicle.%20Give%20some%20of%20the%20plastic%20pieces%20on%20the%20center%20console%20and%20front%20dash%20a%20tap%2C%20and%20they%20sound%20hollow%20and%20a%20bit%20flimsy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20biggest%20change%20in%20the%20Rogues'%20cabin%20is%20the%20addition%20of%20this%20new%20optional%2012.3-inch%20touch-sensitive%20infotainment%20screen%20that%20replaces%20the%20old%209-inch%20unit.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223470%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google%20Maps%20runs%20on%20Apple%20CarPlay%20on%20the%202024%20Nissan%20Rogue%20SL's%2012.3-inch%20infotainment%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667ec00cd1c84a0eaca8a2a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222602%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20CarPlay%20on%20the%20Rogue's%2012.3-inch%20infotainment%20screen.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EScreen%20quality%20excellent%20and%20Nissan's%20updated%20infotainment%20system%20proved%20to%20be%20intuitive%20and%20with%20quick%20response%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20trim%20levels%20still%20get%20the%20standard%208-inch%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Rogue%20comes%20with%20wireless%20Apple%20CarPlay%20and%20Android%20Auto%20along%20with%20Google%20Assist%20integration.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20screen%20is%20also%20home%20to%20the%20Rogue%20SL's%20surround%20view%20camera.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223599%5C%22%2