cted-13160732%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98An%20Accident%2C%2020%20Surgeries%20%26amp%3B%2010%25%20Chance%20to%20Live%E2%80%99%3A%20Nothing%20Could%20Kill%20My%20Dream%20of%20Becoming%20a%20Doctor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mention%20of%20accident%2C%20physical%20injury%20and%20trauma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20inspire%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20could%20do%20it%2C%20I%20can%20too.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20walk%20again%20because%20of%20you.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20gratifying%20things%20to%20hear.%20And%20Dr%20Sakshi%20Maheshwari%E2%80%99s%20day%20is%20flooded%20with%20them.%20The%2027-year-old%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F216984%2Fhow-to-protect-knee-pain-surgery-total-replacement-partial-arthritis-padma-shri-surgeon-dr-ashok-rajgopal-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorthopaedic%20surgeon%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20%E2%80%98hope%20in%20human%20form%E2%80%99%20for%20her%20patients%20at%20the%20Civil%20Hospital%2C%20Ahmedabad%3B%20they%20see%20her%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20a%20new%20lease%20on%20life%2C%20heralding%20her%20a%20miracle%20worker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESakshi%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20this%20feeling.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20only%20seven%20years%20ago%20that%20she%20looked%20at%20her%20surgeons%20through%20the%20same%20lens%20when%20she%20spent%20months%20at%20the%20Manipal%20Hospital%20after%20a%20life-threatening%20accident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20sits%20down%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20recall%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20toughest%20phases%20of%20her%20life%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20finds%20it%20almost%20impossible%20to%20relive%20the%20details.%20This%20is%20due%20to%20two%20reasons%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20Sakshi%20was%20unconscious%20for%