%20grow%20vegetables!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditional%20crops%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat%20have%20longer%20growth%20cycles%20which%20are%20generally%20twice%20a%20year.%20Vegetable%20farming%2C%20however%2C%20gives%20multiple%20harvests%20as%20the%20growth%20cycles%20are%20shorter%20and%20are%20more%20profitable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVegetable%20farming%20offers%20a%20triple%20win%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351525%2Ffarming-profitable-how-to-make-natural-pesticides-himachal-couple-zero-budget-natural-earns-double%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigher%20income%20for%20farmers%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20traders%2C%20enhanced%20consumer%20health%20and%20a%20rejuvenated%20economy.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20when%20vegetables%20rise%2C%20people%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dilip%20Rajan%2C%20the%20chief%20operating%20officer%20at%20the%20East-West%20Seed%20Global%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmarika%20realised%20this%20fact%20and%20first%20worked%20on%20getting%20the%20land%20ready%20for%20vegetable%20cultivation.%20The%20first%20vegetable%20she%20grew%20was%20tomato%2C%20seeking%20help%20from%20an%20agricultural%20consultant%20to%20make%20the%20transition%20smooth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201599px)%20100vw%2C%201599px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika2-1719549343.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smarika%20has%20harvested%20tomato%20in%20over%2013%20acres.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika2-1719549343.jpeg%201599w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika2-1719549343-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika2-