3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20recall%20how%20in%202016%2C%20Panjab%20University%20made%20headlines%20for%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20first%20public%20universities%20in%20India%20to%20build%20a%20separate%20washroom%20for%20trans%20students%20on%20campus.%20If%20you%E2%80%99re%20looking%20for%20the%20source%20of%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338067%2Fbengaluru-transwoman-helps-abandoned-eldery-orphans-food-shelter-ngo-nammane-summane-impact-appeal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevolutionary%20step%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20look%20no%20further%20than%20Dhananjay%2C%20who%20still%20carries%20her%20moniker%20of%20being%20%E2%80%98Chandigarh%E2%80%99s%20first%20transgender%20student%E2%80%99%20with%20great%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20conversation%20with%20her%20reveals%2C%20right%20from%20the%20onset%2C%20Dhananjay%20has%20attempted%20to%20break%20glass%20ceilings%20whenever%20she%20comes%20across%20one.%20And%20the%20food%20truck%20that%20she%20runs%20from%205%20pm%20to%2011%20pm%20every%20evening%20is%20no%20exception.%20In%20the%20minutes%20she%20has%20to%20spare%20between%20doling%20out%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20spring%20rolls%2C%20pasta%2C%20fried%20rice%2C%20noodles%20and%20other%20delicious%20fast%20food%20to%20the%20many%20patrons%20who%20flock%20to%20the%20truck%2C%20Dhananjay%20lets%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%20on%20how%20a%20trans%20identity%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20translate%20to%20giving%20up%20on%20one%E2%80%99s%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20food%20truck%20could%20speak%2C%20it%20would%20have%20a%20compelling%20tale%20to%20tell.%20In%20June%202021%2C%20actor%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%20who%20was%20promoting%20his%20film%20%E2%80%98Chandigarh%20Kare%20Aashiqui%E2%80%99%20first%20donated%20the%20truck%20to%20Dhananjay.%20However%2C%20what%20was%20meant%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20her%20be%20financially%20independent%20had%20th