ral%20setup.%20We%20were%20done%20with%20the%20hustle%20of%20city%20life%20and%20wanted%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20makes%20us%20happy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20the%20couple%20moved%20to%20the%20picturesque%20Nilgiris%20mountains%20with%20an%20idea%20to%20live%20off%20grid%2C%20surrounded%20by%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20built%20our%20home%20with%20our%20own%20hands%20using%20mud%20andstarted%20growing%20our%20own%20food%2C%20harvesting%20water%20from%20mountain%20streams%20and%20harnessing%20solar%20energy%20for%20electricity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20couple%20switched%20to%20a%20sustainable%20and%20minimalistic%20lifestyle%2C%20they%20observed%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20same%20lifestyle%20was%20a%20struggle%20for%20rural%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20we%20lived%20in%20the%20same%20surroundings%2C%20our%20lives%20were%20so%20different%20and%20stable%20because%20of%20our%20savings.%20But%20livelihood%20was%20an%20everyday%20challenge%20for%20the%20tribal%20people%20living%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suhas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20informs%20that%20agriculture%20was%20not%20the%20main%20occupation%20in%20the%20region%20and%20tourism%20also%20remained%20affected.%20%E2%80%9COther%20than%20tea%20picking%2C%20there%20was%20no%20other%20regular%20work%20for%20rural%20women.%20Every%20morning%2C%20they%20would%20leave%20their%20homes%20and%20kids%20behind%20to%20work%20in%20other%20villages%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20give%20back%20to%20the%20community%2C%20who%20were%20now%20their%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frag-dolls-1-1719483011.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20the%20startup%2C%20Suni