20Advocating%20for%20parent%20education%20as%20an%20accessible%20fundamental%20right%20across%20all%20socio-economic%20groups%20is%20crucial.%20By%20supporting%20parents%20in%20raising%20their%20children%2C%20we%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20better%20world%20and%20a%20better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(This%20article%20is%20written%20by%20Kesang%20Menezes%20of%20Parenting%20Matters%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%3Cem%3E%20Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EParenting%20Matters%20is%20deeply%20committed%20to%20building%20a%20world%20where%20children%20can%20thrive%20to%20their%20fullest%20potential.%20They%20believe%20that%20informed%20and%20connected%20parenting%20is%20crucial%20for%20individual%20growth%2C%20community%20well-being%2C%20and%20societal%20progress.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETheir%20core%20mission%20is%20to%20empower%20parents%20to%20create%20nurturing%20families.%20With%20a%20team%20of%2012%20certified%20parent%20educators%20having%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%2C%20they%20have%20transformed%20the%20lives%20of%20over%201%20lakh%20families.%20Parenting%20Matters%20equips%20parents%20with%20the%20latest%20knowledge%20and%20essential%20skills%20through%20workshops%2C%20courses%2C%20talks%2C%20and%20articles.%20They%20focus%20on%20providing%20insights%20into%20brain%20and%20child%20development%2C%20alongside%20offering%20strategies%20for%20fostering%20positive%20communication%20and%20effective%20discipline.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWorking%20with%20parents%20across%20diverse%20groups%20in%20multiple%20languages%20in%20schools%20(both%20private%20and%20government)%2C%20corporates%2C%20and%20at%20an%20individual%20level%2C%20Parenting%20Matters%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20conviction%20that%20by%20supporting%20families%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20transformation%20towards%20a%20healthier%20and%20more%20caring%20community%2C%20one%20family%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719408628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parenting%20Matters%20has%20been%20working%20with%20parents%20for%20over%2020%20years%20to%20help%20them%20figure%20out%20effective%20and%20sensitive%20ways%20to%20raise%20their%20children.%20Their%20main%20focus%20is%20to%20undo%20the%20past%20where%20anger%2C%20intolerance%2C%20and%20disrespect%20governed%20parent-children%20relationships.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354393%2Fhow-to-improve-your-parenting-skills-ten-lessons-tips-tricks-from-parents-parenting-matters-workshops%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Assam%2C%20Solar%20Energy%20Helps%20Doctors%20%26amp%3B%20Medicines%20Reach%20Island%20Dwellers%20on%20Boats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20June%2C%20check%20out%20our%20%23ApnaGharSolar%20series%2C%20an%20exclusive%20deep%20dive%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.solarsquare.in%2F%3Futm_source%3Dsocialmedia%26utm_medium%3Dad%26utm_campaign%3DTheBetterIndia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESolarSquare%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20solar%20power%20boom.%20Stay%20tuned%20for%20more%20interesting%20stories%2C%20data%20and%20information!%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Saddam%20Hussain%20from%20Silchar%20left%20his%20home%20around%207%20am%20for%20his%20camp%20duty%20in%20Sadhu%20Sapori%20village%20of%20Majuli%20district%20%E2%80%93%20a%20large%20river%20island%20formed%20by%20the%20majestic%20Brahmaputra%20river%20and%20its%20tributaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20four%20hours%20of%20the%20boat%20ride%2C%20Dr%20Saddam%20reached%20the%20village%20along%20with%20his%20team%20of%20healthcare%20workers.%20It%20was%20not%20the%20regular%20OPD%20clinic%20of%20a%20city%20hospital.%20Here%2C%20the%20camp%20was%20set-up%20by%20the%20river%20bank.%20The%20community%20is%20always%20delighted%20to%20see%20the%20healthcare%20workers%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20morning%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20at%20least%2050%20patients%20who%20complained%20of%20abdominal%20pain%2C%20urinary%20tract%20infections%2C%20hypertension%2C%20joint%20pains%2C%20skin%20related%20diseases%3B%20and%20those%20who%20required%20antenatal%20care%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Saddam%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20healthcare%20gap%20in%20the%20region%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20flooding%20of%20the%20Brahmaputra%20river%20affects%20a%20large%20population%20residing%20in%20the%20islands.%20Whenever%20it%20rains%20heavily%20in%20Arunachal%2C%20the%20river%20water%20rises.%20There%20are%20no%20sub-centres%20in%20the%20islands.%20We%20are%20the%20only%20healthcare%20workers%20for%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-2-1719399558.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Riturekha%20says%20that%20with%20solar%20energy%2C%20the%20crew%20has%20an%20uninterrupted%20power%20supply%20for%20a%20long%20time.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-2-1719399558.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-2-1719399558-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-2-1719399558-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-2-1719399558-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-2-1719399558-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354366%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERiturekha%20says%20that%20with%20solar%20energy%2C%20the%20crew%20has%20an%20uninterrupted%20power%20supply%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20focus%20on%20routine%20immunisation%2C%20primary%20healthcare%20services%2C%20child%20and%20antenatal%20care%2C%20the%20team%20rows%20from%20village%20to%20village%20across%20the%20district%20organising%20health%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrimary%20healthcare%20was%20a%20distant%20dream%20for%20the%20remote%20riverine%20community%20until%202009%20when%20floating%20health%20clinics%20were%20introduced.%20Prior%20to%20this%2C%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20rural%20residents%20remained%20isolated%20in%20want%20of%20healthcare%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20these%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348884%2Fsenior-citizens-healthcare-boat-clinic-in-sundarbans-shis-foundation-abdul-wohab-sabitri-pal%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboat%20clinics%20%3C%2Fa%3Eharness%20solar%20energy%20to%20efficiently%20run%20the%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20impact-driven%20project%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brains%20behind%20this%20project%20was%20Sanjoy%20Hazarika%2C%20a%20journalist%20and%20filmmaker%20who%20started%20the%20non-profit%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F6801%2Fhope-floats-assams-boat-clinics-help-women-plan-families%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECentre%20for%20North%20East%20Studies%20and%20Policy%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E%20(C-NES)%2C%20driven%20by%20the%20tragedy%20he%20had%20witnessed%20on%20a%20ferry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20work%2C%20I%20kept%20travelling%20to%20rural%20remote%20corners%20and%20observed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20sustained%20healthcare%20system%20in%20these%20islands.%20I%20also%20came%20across%20a%20case%20of%20a%20young%20woman%20who%20died%20during%20childbirth%20on%20the%20ferry.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20whole%20thing%20hit%20me%20pretty%20hard%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20boat%20clinics%20are%20equipped%20with%20vaccines%20for%20newborn%20babies%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20measles%2C%20Japanese%20encephalitis%2C%20polio%2C%20etc.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354368%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20boat%20clinics%20are%20equipped%20with%20vaccines%20for%20newborn%20babies%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20measles%2C%20Japanese%20encephalitis%2C%20polio%2C%20etc.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAssam%E2%80%99s%20maternal%20mortality%20ratio%20was%20also%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20country%20back%20then%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20so%20even%20today%20despite%20the%20slight%20improvement%20%5B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fnada%2Findex.php%2Fcatalog%2F44379%2Fdownload%2F48052%2FSRS_MMR_Bulletin_2018_2020.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E195%20per%20100%2C000%20live%20births%3C%2Fa%3E%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Assam%2C%20there%20are%202%2C500%20islands%20and%20most%20of%20them%20are%20inhabited.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20on%20an%20idea%20that%20involved%20the%20support%20of%20local%20people%20and%20the%20state%20government%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20these%20people%20and%20improve%20the%20health%20conditions%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20vulnerable%20communities%2C%20especially%20the%20women%20and%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%E2%80%99t%20build%20roads%20everywhere%20and%20certainly%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20helicopters%20give%20services%20throughout%20the%20year.%20So%2C%20we%20shifted%20to%20the%20traditional%20system%20of%20using%20boats%20and%20to%20look%20upon%20the%20river%20as%20an%20ally%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sanjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20collaboration%20with%20the%20National%20Rural%20Health%20Mission%2C%20the%20non-profit%20launched%20the%20boat%20clinics%20in%202005%20to%20bridge%20the%20healthcare%20divide.%20Since%20then%2C%20monthly%20health%20camps%20have%20been%20organised%20across%2014%20districts%20including%20Dibrugarh%2C%20Tinsukia%2C%20Jorhat%2FMajuli%2C%20Sonitpur%2C%20and%20Nalbari.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20purpose%2C%2015%20such%20floating%20health%20clinics%20are%20operating%20along%20the%20river%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20isolated%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%2C%20a%20team%20comprising%20two%20medical%20officers%2C%20laboratory%20technician%2C%20pharmacist%2C%20and%20three%20nurses%20reach%20out%20to%20offer%20primary%20healthcare%20at%20the%20island%20itself.%20These%20boat%20