trong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20we%20have%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20boats%20for%2018%20days%20in%20a%20month.%20The%20boat%20was%20our%20home.%20So%2C%20while%20patients%20go%20back%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20we%20could%20not.%20We%20slept%20in%20our%20respective%20beddings%20here%2C%20far%20away%20from%20the%20comforts%20of%20our%20homes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20kerosene-based%20generators%20for%20power%20but%20it%20would%20only%20help%20for%203%20to%204%20hours%20in%20a%20day.%20It%20would%20become%20challenging%20and%20uneasy%20for%20us%20to%20live%20on%20the%20boat%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20summer%20heat.%20Secondly%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20any%20cold%20storage%20facility%20for%20vaccines.%20Having%20a%20permanent%20energy%20supply%20was%20crucial%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20non-profit%20decided%20to%20harness%20solar%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20C-NES%20partnered%20with%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F114009%2Fboat-clinics-brahmaputra-healthcare-boat-clinics-switching-solar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESELCO%20Foundation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20works%20to%20bring%20sustainable%20energy%20solutions%20to%20rural%20and%20urban%20communities%20in%20the%20country.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20the%20large%20boats%20were%20equipped%20with%20solar%20panels%20of%203%20KV%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20solar%20power%20can%E2%80%99t%20drive%20vessels%20on%20a%20river%20as%20powerful%20as%20the%20Brahmaputra.%20So%2C%20we%20use%20it%20to%20run%20lighting%20and%20basic%20services%20like%20fans.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20the%20cold%20chains%20for%20chilling%20units%20which%20store%20and%20carry%20vaccines%20and%20other%20life-saving%20equipment%20are%20also%20solar-powered%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Sanjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdi