c%2C%20shares%20Saurabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20of%20the%20pen%20is%20made%20of%20bamboo%20and%20the%20cap%20is%20made%20of%20coconut%20shell%20%E2%80%94%20this%20simple%20yet%20effective%20approach%20has%20allowed%20him%20to%20create%20pens%20that%20are%20both%20sustainable%20and%20functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20experimented%20from%202018%20to%202020%20before%20finally%20narrowing%20down%20to%20one%20design.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20tried%20various%20methods%20to%20reduce%20and%20eliminate%20plastic%20in%20pens.%20We%20conducted%20numerous%20trials%2C%20each%20requiring%20extensive%20testing%20for%20shelf%20life%2C%20which%20must%20be%2018%20months.%20Each%20test%20took%20around%20six%20months%20to%20yield%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFinally%2C%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20we%20achieved%20a%20breakthrough.%20Our%20current%20method%20allows%20us%20to%20produce%20pens%20with%20an%2018-month%20shelf%20life%20without%20plastic.%20This%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20our%20journey%20toward%20sustainable%20stationery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20pens%20are%20available%20for%20bulk%20purchase%20by%20businesses.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20sold%2020%2C000%20pens%20and%20hopes%20to%20increase%20this%20number%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20sports%20professional%20and%20a%20team%20member%20of%20Youth%20For%20Climate%20India%2C%20used%20the%20biodegradable%20pen.%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20an%20environment%20advocate%2C%20climate%20change%20and%20plastic%20pollution%20deeply%20concern%20me.%20I%20have%20a%20bag%20full%20of%20refills%20of%20pens%20that%20I%20used.%20While%20the%20problem%20seems%20small%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20an%20alternative.%20When%20I%20found%20out%20about%20Saurabh%E2%80%99s%20innovation%2C%20I%20was%20intrigued%20and%20bought%20two%20pens%20from%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20cla